        <h2><a href="/social-media-marketing/should-you-be-blogging-on-linkedin/" data-f-stream-pos="30" data-f-stream-eff-pos="30">Should You Be Blogging on LinkedIn?</a></h2>
            </header>
    <ul class="articleinfo">
        <li>By <span itemprop="author">Business.com Editorial Staff</span></li>

        
        

                   <li class="break"><span class="streampageLink"><a href="/social-media-marketing/">Social Media Marketing</a></span></li>
            </ul>
    <p>Even if you aren&#039;t a Bill Gates or Richard Branson, your blog posts on LinkedIn can still reach a substantial audience and create exposure.</p>
</article>
